531
00:32:22,149 --> 00:32:26,153
I am told my grandson was doing 
a bit of mischief. I'm really sorry.

532
00:32:26,253 --> 00:32:27,855
Are you an ocean seal? A monkey?

533
00:32:27,855 --> 00:32:29,256
Who threw this out?

534
00:32:29,256 --> 00:32:30,758
I guess we can't throw trash out now...

535
00:32:30,758 --> 00:32:31,759
This is trash?

536
00:32:31,759 --> 00:32:33,560
Whatever it is that is uncomfortable,
feel free to tell.

537
00:32:33,661 --> 00:32:36,864
If you could lend us a pot, so we could
cook something to eat...

538
00:32:37,264 --> 00:32:39,066
Better know that this is all because 
your mom is a good one.

539
00:32:39,166 --> 00:32:39,867
CEO sir?

540
00:32:39,867 --> 00:32:41,368
Yes, are you doing fine?

541
00:32:41,368 --> 00:32:42,369
And you, CEO sir?

542
00:32:42,369 --> 00:32:43,771
Shall we cajole Na Jin A into it?

543
00:32:43,771 --> 00:32:45,773
Even if we make her come to our side,
if she fails, we're finished.

544
00:32:45,773 --> 00:32:47,274
Sister-in-law, come in and
take care of business.

545
00:32:47,274 --> 00:32:48,075
Whatever.

546
00:32:48,075 --> 00:32:48,876
No!
Please go back.

547
00:32:48,876 --> 00:32:51,579
She just wants to use a bathroom. 
Even that isn't allowed?

548
00:32:51,579 --> 00:32:54,081
Is this family into playing with people or what?

